app-role.description:
Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the Development projects in any program:
 - view project data (key data, study data, costs, import log, resources, PTR and etc.);
 - view Current and Approved plan versions;
 - view discrepancy report of the project plan version.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the Development projects:
 - move any inactive project of any program to the Recycle Bin;
 - Delete any project from the Recycle Bin.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the Development projects:
 - edit project data (key data, study data, PTR, and etc.) in any program;
 - edit project Raw plan.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the Development projects in any program:
 - publish project Raw or Current plan;
 - change publication comment.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the  Development projects in the assigned program:
 - publish Raw or Current Plan version;
 - change publication comment.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the Development projects in the assigned program:
 - view project data (key data, study data, costs, import log, PTR, and etc.);
 - view Raw/Current/Approved plan versions; 
 - view discrepancy reports of the project plan version.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the tag-specific LE meeting form:
 - set default probabilistic LE values;
 - provide/refine LE values.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the Development projects in any program:
 - view project Raw plan;
 - view discrepancy report of the project plan.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the Development projects in any program:
 - assign project ID via work item;
 - edit project ID.

Grants access to the following functionality that is subject to the D2 projects:
 - move any inactive D2 project to the Recycle Bin;
